collection

Interface BinaryTree<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of the elements stored in this collection.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<E>, Iterable<E>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    SortedBinaryTree<E>

    public interface BinaryTree<E>
extends Collection<E>
    Defines behavior needed to process elements in a binary tree. Still similar in practice to a generic collection.
    Author:
    Jacob Malter
